Cook veggie burger according to package directions. Top hot burger with cheese slice. Let stand for 1 minute or until cheese melts. Meanwhile, in small bowl, stir together mayonnaise and pesto. Serve burger in focaccia along with mayonnaise mixture, roasted pepper and fresh basil leaves. ON THE GRILL: Preheat grill. Use a food thermometer to be sure patties reach minimum internal temperature of 160 degrees F.